data.description: Here is your wonderfully situated two-story on a quiet block convenient to everything.  Your solid starter home has a fenced in backyard for Fido, a two car garage that will save you time on winter mornings, a convenient mudroom off the back when you come in, a sun filled southern facing porch, central air to keep you cool on hot summer days and all your bedrooms are on one level. There is a bonus room to use for whatever you dream up. Closet? Nursery? Storage? You get to decide. There is pristine and untouched natural woodwork with a gorgeous buffet and open staircase. This is a solid house and it feels like home.  Come with your own decorating ideas and make it yours!
